{"tid":2456734,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【毒病進化？】法國變種病毒能躲過核酸檢測 染疫8人全死","createTime":"2021-03-22T06:56:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-23T15:29:28.000Z","uid":293677,"like":37,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"29913e1be5f6c9c30b519172ace43c1b93f79f2b","tid":2456734,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:56:30.000Z","msg":"2021/03/22 14:39<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕法國西北部布列塔尼大區（Brittany）上週證實出現全新的武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）變種病毒。<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">經初步分析，該變種病毒似乎能躲過一般的PCR核酸檢測，最新的消息傳出，8名感染者已全部死亡，初步顯示該病毒株傳染力恐較全球其他變種毒株更強，也比原先預期更致命！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n據法國《快訊報》（Ladepeche）報導，3月13日，當地濱海城市拉尼永（Lannion）的一家醫院發現了79例COVID-19病毒感染病例，其中8例帶有該病毒變種，這8宗案例中，7名患者原本都順利通過核酸測試，判定為陰性。最終，研究人員透過對感染者的血液樣本和呼吸系統組織進行檢測，才發現了這款新型變種毒株<br />\n<br />\n科學家將這款法國變種病毒命名為「le variant breton（不列塔尼變種毒株）」。布列塔尼一直是法國武肺確診病例最少的地區之一，「不列塔尼變種毒株」被發現後，外界開始猜測，該地區的確診人數少，可能與新變種毒株能逃過核酸檢測有關。<br />\n<br />\n專家們的初步研究結果顯示，「le variant breton」毒株的毒性或傳染性比此前已在全球各地發現的其他變種毒株更強。<br />\n<br />\n目前，科學家們正在針對這款新的變種毒株做進一步風險研究，驗證該毒株對已開發的疫苗以及曾感染病毒者體內抗體的反應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3475020\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3475020&d=Hu0SY4Cx1oodln7cCHpxbf3PLjr3aI%2Bxco%2FW%2FCjCBac%3D&h=52023c03\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3475020&h=968e7a60\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3475020</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\"><span class=\"x-large\">中国病毒真係CLS</span></span>"},{"pid":"833c05037a845de374a5542d7020700b4a71d8bf","tid":2456734,"uid":147376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:57:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"757888c2240fc5651771cfc461c28120c275a167","tid":2456734,"uid":226955,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:00:05.000Z","msg":"武漢肺炎 - 戰爭用生化病毒果然名不虛傳"},{"pid":"1a6cbc64708d2bee55e57970f5df7cac2b7ddbd8","tid":2456734,"uid":32028,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:01:21.000Z","msg":"英國變種病毒<br />\n南非變種病毒<br />\n巴西變種病毒<br />\n法國變種病毒<br />\n<br />\n就係無武漢病毒"},{"pid":"bd782d84235876ee462d3afd0396049c756f701e","tid":2456734,"uid":50502,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:01:30.000Z","msg":"陷球剷了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"658dc0af65619a1cb6151cff23feb12d427965d5","tid":2456734,"uid":288158,"like":7,"dislike":9,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:01:59.000Z","msg":"連登仔：弱感冒就弱感冒啦恐懼撚"},{"pid":"783e52fc0d4e943de6fd2689141a2878d6800443","tid":2456734,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:02:25.000Z","msg":"人類滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce01571fff97bfd60018e88d23c549b6bccc872f","tid":2456734,"uid":270098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:03:21.000Z","msg":"resident evil"},{"pid":"392aa0170484e4723b3995a2a98456159de23d7b","tid":2456734,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:04:06.000Z","msg":"估法國一早有份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08980d5ad674683e06eb2c44ed0e43f6e54fe7c3","tid":2456734,"uid":256246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T07:06:01.000Z","msg":"打科興得永生<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6466fe4790b7f1524070bcaaab8ccc757